  "description": "Two Sine oscillators separated by an octave (src2 tuned +12 semitones), drawn together by a strong 7-limit gravitational field (fieldStrength=0.8, fieldRate=0.02). The faster field rate means quicker correction to just ratios. Chorus adds shimmer and spatial width. When notes cluster near JI ratios they lock — when played far apart the gravity becomes audible as a bending force.",
